    "body": "> Hi @ajsutton can i pick this, also need clarity on the below questions.\r\n\r\nYep, that would be great.\r\n\r\n> 1. while fetching the VotedValidatorIndices  is the below code correct ?\r\n\r\nI think the code you're looking at is behind master. `getVotedvalidatorIndices` was replaced with `getHighestVotedValidatorIndex` in https://github.com/ConsenSys/teku/pull/4260 \r\n\r\n>  1. do we want to change the signature for votes everywhere ,  for example consider the below class.\r\n> \r\n> ```java\r\n>   public interface VoteUpdateChannel extends VoidReturningChannelInterface {\r\n> \r\n>   void onVotesUpdated(Map<UInt64, VoteTracker> votes);\r\n> }\r\n> ```\r\n> \r\n> do we want to convert the type of this arg to VoteTracker[]\r\n\r\nNot necessarily everywhere.  In this case it is often only a subset of votes that are being updated and so only the changed votes wind up being passed to this method to update storage. The `Map<UInt64, VoteTracker>` API still works well for this.\r\n",
